    "removal or addition of human-readable text), it is easier to track.",
    "This communication is an integral part of robotic activities on Wikipedia (for an overview, see Zheng et al. 2019) that enables its functionality as a global memory place (Pentzold 2009) and results in the production of memory narratives used by humans.",
    "The major implication of the rise of robot-to-robot memory communication relates to the possibility of robotic agents moving beyond facilitating human remembrance (i.e.",
    "the main function of human-to-robot communication) and engaging in the processes of remembrance on their own (i.e.",
    "independently of human agents)."
